---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cardiomyopathies — Dr Delhasse, Cardiologist" description="Diagnosis of cardiomyopathies: dilated, rigid or thickened heart. Genetic assessment and specialist management." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="text-primary">Cardiomyopathies</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Diseases of the heart muscle</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/svg/expertise/Cardiomyopathies.svg" alt="Cardiomyopathies" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>Cardiomyopathy is a disease of the heart muscle that impairs its ability to pump blood effectively, potentially leading to heart failure.</p>

      <p>Cardiomyopathies present in several forms including a dilated heart, a rigid heart, a thickened heart, or replacement of heart muscle with fatty tissue. These conditions appear at various ages, including in young people. Symptoms often result from complications such as arrhythmias or heart failure.</p>

      <p>The causes are multiple but often genetic, which recommends family screening for cases with a family history. Acquired forms can develop during one's lifetime. Cardiologists often use advanced diagnostics, particularly magnetic resonance imaging.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/areas-of-expertise" class="btn btn--outline">&larr; All areas</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
